{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"663","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"綠債發行 今年拚增200億元","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>2020-03-29 22:28 </span><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>經濟日報<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>記者王奐敏<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>台北報導</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>截至<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>29</span>日止，國內綠色債券流通在外共計<span lang='EN-US'>39</span>檔，合計發行餘額為新台幣<span lang='EN-US'>1,094.22</span>億元，綠色債券發行總金額已逾千億元。櫃買中心表示，第<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>季有四檔合計<span lang='EN-US'>70</span>億元的綠債新發行，上半年新發行綠債有機會逾<span lang='EN-US'>100</span>億元，全年目標上看<span lang='EN-US'>200</span>億元。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>今年綠色債券的發行由國內銀行率先開跑，兆豐國際商業銀行於<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>11</span>日完成發行三年期，票面利率<span lang='EN-US'>0.6%</span>，發行金額為新台幣<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>億元的綠色債券，所募資金主要用於太陽能、風力發電、電動車、廢棄物處理利用，以及汙水下水道系統興建等綠色投資計畫放款，符合「再生能源及能源科技發展」、「溫室氣體減量」、「汙染防治與控制」及 「水資源節約、潔淨或回收循環再利用」等類別。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>另東方匯理銀行台北分行、第一商業銀行及玉山銀行亦分別於<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>20</span>日、<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>日及<span lang='EN-US'>11</span>日取得綠色債券資格認可，皆已於<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月底前完成發行及上櫃，玉山銀行<span lang='EN-US'>19</span>日發行<span lang='EN-US'>30</span>億元綠債，東方匯理銀行台北分行、第一商業銀行<span lang='EN-US'>27</span>日分別發行<span lang='EN-US'>20</span>億元、<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>億元綠債。第<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>季合計有四檔，<span lang='EN-US'>70</span>億元的新綠債發行。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>在配合政府能源結構轉型之目標，以及因應國內離岸風電開發之資金需求下，今年除本國銀行及外國銀行在台分行外，國營事業及外國離岸風電開發商也將有機會持續發行綠色債券。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://udn.com/news/story/7254/4452856?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-03-30","clk_count":"122"}},"__N_SSG":true}